17
00:02:22.851 --> 00:02:25.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
東西新聞社が 我々同様―

18
00:02:25.145 --> 00:02:28.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
世界のジャーナリズムの
