25
00:02:49.586 --> 00:02:50.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ええ それでは―

26
00:02:50.545 --> 00:02:54.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
日本料理の醍醐味(だいごみ)を
