27
00:02:54.674 --> 00:02:56.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（拍手）
（ショーバン）フッフッフッフ…

28
00:02:56.384 --> 00:02:58.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
日本料理の醍醐味…

29
00:02:58.386 --> 00:03:00.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
とんだ お笑いぐさだ

30
00:03:00.722 --> 00:03:01.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
