66
00:05:02.510 --> 00:05:04.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああ この香り！

67
00:05:04.262 --> 00:05:08.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
