できるキノコで―

70
00:05:14.605 --> 00:05:17.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
豚に嗅ぎ当てさせて
探し出すのですが

71
00:05:17.567 --> 00:05:18.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
